 * ## Audit category overview
 * | Audit category                 | Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
 * | ------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
